司署擔任檢察官一職。他先後於1979年及1984年獲委任為高級檢察官及副首席檢察官。他於1984年在香港取得大律師資格，並於1985年獲委任為御用大律師。於1987年至1991年期間，他出任法律政策專員。<br />\n<br />\n司徒敬法官於1991年加入本港司法機構出任高等法院暫委法官。他於1992年獲委任為高等法院法官，並於2000年獲委任為上訴法庭法官。於2009年至2014年期間，他出任上訴法庭副庭長。"},{"pid":"376cac0778fe94e76872929c1cabec6665cf8def","tid":2382243,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"法官都可以自己揀，俾你玩晒佢囉！"},{"pid":"24c7f46eb5aed074ba4053f1b3ab3d00426f5e23","tid":2382243,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"376cac0778fe94e76872929c1cabec6665cf8def","tid":2382243,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"法官都可以自己揀，俾你玩晒佢囉！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849482ae6c3c3c25c5c5c2bbc2f8ea612110e64d","tid":2382243,"uid":260121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e0202767792d9035aede88fdd7308fe8a0d3f0","tid":2382243,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24c7f46eb5aed074ba4053f1b3ab3d00426f5e23","tid":2382243,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"376cac0778fe94e76872929c1cabec6665cf8def","tid":2382243,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"法官都可以自己揀，俾你玩晒佢囉！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:28:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"香港法律給蟈安和黑警搞到面目全非"},{"pid":"bc1605f57e9978eb4be7e2c04f59073465cee3dd","tid":2382243,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"849482ae6c3c3c25c5c5c2bbc2f8ea612110e64d","tid":2382243,"uid":260121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4bb52966c0cd34ecac63b9f6cbabd012ffca889","tid":2382243,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6NL8LgJWzx1EnncqP3vKSXy7k4w=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3LXOT7OVZZBZHF7DYGY7GKPXUY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6NL8LgJWzx1EnncqP3vKSXy7k4w%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3LXOT7OVZZBZHF7DYGY7GKPXUY.jpg&h=353efdbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒創辦人黎智英在欺詐和勾結外國勢力案件獲批保釋，律政司堅持上訴，終審法院受理上訴，並接納律政司申請，暫時將黎智英再度還柙，以待2月1日正審。司法機構網頁公佈，正審除了上次有份參與聆訊的時任常任法官、現任首席法官張舉能以及常任法官李義外，常任法官霍兆剛、非常任法官陳兆愷及司徒敬亦會審理本案。換言之，終審法院再多三名法官獲公開國安法指定法官身份。<br />\n<br />\n終審法院現時有兩名常任法官，均參與本案聆訊。另外，終院現時有4名本港非常任法官及14名海外非常任法官，而本案兩名非常任法官均屬本港法官。終院將於下月1日上午10時審理本案，預計需時一天。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/6V32KEYWCJHLRBQOKKYPJOTLL4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2F6V32KEYWCJHLRBQOKKYPJOTLL4%2F&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdny1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=05762263\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2F6V32KEYWCJHLRBQOKKYPJOTLL4%2F&h=50672cf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/6V32KEYWCJHLRBQOKKYPJOTLL4/</a>"},{"pid":"cb3679416c47c39cead5690e387622ada3299d71","tid":2382243,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:40:14.000Z","msg":"是旦啦，就算判可以保釋轉頭又話有權直接送中，根本個coin兩面都係公！"},{"pid":"aacf177c27da337b1f1cb82b8e2957877ea19eaa","tid":2382243,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:52:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/about/who/judges/npjs/index_id_5.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout%2Fwho%2Fjudges%2Fnpjs%2Findex_id_5.html&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdny1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=825b7957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/about/who/judges/npjs/index_id_5.html</a><br />\n司徒敬法官於1945年在<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">非洲羅德西亞</span></span>出生........."},{"pid":"a45253114cdc89ab0a18aa9da8de74542856cc70","tid":2382243,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb3679416c47c39cead5690e387622ada3299d71","tid":2382243,"uid":7369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:40:14.000Z","msg":"是旦啦，就算判可以保釋轉頭又話有權直接送中，根本個coin兩面都係公！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b2c46c969985460f40d7483b7a954df18ffeea","t